---
title: Barbecue Pork Schnitzel with Lemon Crushed Potatoes & Beetroot Relish
description: A classic schnitzel is always best served with a side of potatoes. We’re jazzing things up tonight by crushing the potatoes with a
squeeze of lemon juice. Crumb the pork with the barbecue seasoning for a smokey flavour, then serve with a sweet and vibrant
beetroot relish.

